    "description": "魔女们在天上保护着人间的秩序，创世以来，就是如此。<br>然而，小魔女洛瑞塔穿越时间，带来了让魔女们不安的神谕，并且也让她不得不（再一次）踏上命中注定的冒险旅途。这一次，她能成功吗？<br>这是有史以来第一位时间魔女、以及她的朋友们的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/cd57cc5107d984c640e83d7436592090.poster.avif?t=1697308843\" width=630 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/cd57cc5107d984c640e83d7436592090.webm?t=1697308843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/cd57cc5107d984c640e83d7436592090.mp4?t=1697308843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>《时间切片：序章》是一款2D平台跳跃解谜游戏。扮演可爱的魔女洛瑞塔，在魔法学院中，利用移动、跳跃、记录与回溯时间、发射魔法弹等技巧，解开各种各样的谜题。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >视觉表现</h2>《时间切片：序章》有精心绘制的场景、人物美术表现。当主角发动时间魔法时，场景的视觉表现更会发生惊奇的变化。在美丽而壮观的魔法学园中一探究竟吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/aeb83533535974cc88e6a9f30bf80c02.poster.avif?t=1697308843\" width=630 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/aeb83533535974cc88e6a9f30bf80c02.webm?t=1697308843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/aeb83533535974cc88e6a9f30bf80c02.mp4?t=1697308843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事内容</h2>体验以AVG等形式展现的丰富剧情，感受魔女们的友情故事。每位角色均有精美的立绘展示。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏流程</h2>约60~90分钟的游戏流程中，在美妙的音乐伴随下，游览氛围各异的游戏场景，挑战13个精巧构思的谜题关卡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207540/extras/4005ab9f5d5986d0c28d620c8a4653cc.poster.avif?t=1697308843\"